Initial 404 Errors
Occurred when accessing /doku.php before DokuWiki files were fully in place.
Fix: Verified file paths and ensured files were extracted into /var/www/html/dokuwiki.

“Topic does not exist yet” message
Happened when the start page wasn’t created.
Fix: Created start.txt and copied home.txt contents into it.

Permissions Issues
Apache needed proper access to DokuWiki directories.
Fix: Used chown -R www-data:www-data /var/www/html/dokuwiki.
